\c 4
\s1 Xiiala lɨ́ɨ¹i 'in Espíritu Tyʉ́² tya' Dios joongɨ xiiala lɨ́ɨ¹i 'in sii²¹ anticristo
\p 
\v 1 Tsaru'¹u' 'in 'iin²¹²na, jo jai'² cwolíin²¹naa' jileei'²¹ 'in jin'² 'e faa'²¹o cwáain¹ tya' Dios. Cóon²oon' cwáain¹ coon'¹³ ce tún² 'ee 'e faa'²¹a 'ido. Nuu²uu' wana faa'²¹a cwáain¹ tya' Dios owa jo faa'²¹a 'ee. Rǿø²mo cwoo'¹³ juncwii²¹ coon'¹³ 'in tsá² tajuui²¹ 'in jin'²in 'e faa'²¹o cwáain¹ tya' Dios pe jo jo'².
