\v 5 'In tsá² tajuui²¹ do faa'²¹o jmai'² tya' 'e sá² ni cwoo'¹³ juncwii²¹ tsʉ tɨɨi²¹ jmai' 'e sá² juncwii²¹ lo. Joon lɨ́ɨ¹ tɨ́²‑tsi tsá² taain²¹² juncwii²¹ núu²un júu³ tya'a.
